sub_title: Compliance and Control Analyst for Microsoft at Tricycle Europe
summary:
Freshly graduated from a master’s degree in International Criminal Law, currently in the final stages of my internship as a Compliance & Control Analyst for Tricycle Europe through the Microsoft ECIF program.

My academic foundation in law combined with my demonstrated expertise in customer support and adept stakeholder management position me for a future focused on legal compliance. I'm particularly drawn to the intricate realms of financial crimes/AML, KYC and CDD.

As I start my professional journey, my goal is to contribute meaningfully to the field of legal compliance and continually expand my horizons.
